<HEADLINE>
FT  07 MAY 92 / Rise in number of overseas visitors
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE British Tourist Authority said 900,000 long-haul travellers visited the
UK in the first two months of the year, nearly 50 per cent more than in the
same period last year.
In January and February the total number of overseas visitors was 2.1m, up
18 per cent.
</TEXT>
